headline: Workday Teams Up With Kinaxis to Streamline Operational Silos
summary: WDAY teams up with Kinaxis to unify supply chain, finance and HR data, enabling faster AI-powered decision-making across industries.

headline: WorkBoard Posts Record 1H Growth Accelerated by AI Agents
summary: REDWOOD CITY, Calif., September 15, 2025--WorkBoard today announced record growth in 1H, fueled by executive urgency to improve strategy execution, strong adoption of its new AI agents, and partnerships with Workday and Microsoft. Year over year sales rose 30% and quarter of quarter sales grew 50% in Q2 with 40% of new business from Europe.

headline: Exploring High Growth Tech Stocks in the US Market September 2025
summary: As of September 2025, the U.S. stock market is witnessing a mixed performance with the tech-heavy Nasdaq Composite reaching record highs, driven by strong performances from major tech companies like Tesla and Microsoft. Amidst this backdrop, investors are closely monitoring potential interest rate cuts by the Federal Reserve as inflation data presents a complex picture for economic growth.
